author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Were trying to raise $3000.00 CDN for the Canadian Cancer Society.  A charity focusing on cancer research funding and care for people going through the challenges of Cancer. You can donate here: https://tilt.fyi/VEsKWA1IfP. 

We have tons of Giveaways to happen throughout the stream as well as extra giveaways if we make various fundraising goals.  

Join us for a tons of fun with Gingerbread terrain, giveaways and a 40k game in there as well!

Ultramarines vs Astra Militarum featuring the new detachments.  This should be a ton of fun!
